based on your actual situation.</li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"2" dir=3D"auto">
<li>Volumes Configuration=EF=BC=8CThe application's root directory inside t=
he container is set to /workspace. The default docker-compose.yaml lists so=
me practical examples for uploading/downloading content.</li>
<li>shm_size=EF=BC=9A The default available memory for Docker Desktop on Wi=
ndows is too small, which can cause abnormal operations. Adjust according t=
o your own situation.</li>
<li>Under the deploy section, GPU-related settings should be adjusted cauti=
ously according to your system and actual circumstances.</li>
</ol>
